reviewText: Was not all Timmy and lassie episodes like I thought

These are two classic episodes of Lassie, which were shown on reruns as Jeff's Collie, starring Tommy Rettig (River of No Return, 5,000 Fingers of Dr. T.).  The first is "The Treehouse."  Jeff  & Porky build a treehouse & sleep in it with their dogs; but Porky's hounddog Pokey howls all night, so Jeff kicks them out.  Something mysterious happens to the treehouse and Jeff blames his friend. The second is "The Trial," in which Lassie is put on trial for allegedly biting a boy.
